{"tid":524373,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來紋身師真係好易做","createTime":"2018-01-09T13:42:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T20:46:09.000Z","uid":1774,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ea1fd0b6ac594ed4fd2dd7f6ea789247b57c8e5f","tid":524373,"uid":1774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T13:42:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/213127_c772478e08c9433d93f41dff9dd13a7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F213127_c772478e08c9433d93f41dff9dd13a7e.jpg&h=994cf53b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/213131_0dab4b8e158bbe4560fe2f0290116bf7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F213131_0dab4b8e158bbe4560fe2f0290116bf7.jpg&h=0e6bb7b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前睇個紋身post見到呢位紋身師都幾出名<br />\n果時特登follow左佢<br />\n但佢原來係抄圖...<br />\n果張仲係紋身展嘅poster<br />\n香港紋身師真係好做<br />\n自己設計都慳番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d54ae4104d71733307d90eca5159f3d5dd45abec","tid":524373,"uid":40422,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T13:45:41.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係左抄右抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"848ca9ccf30963ada51b76f3ae7ce2f8630e29f4","tid":524373,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T13:46:07.000Z","msg":"純粹問下  如果係個客拎住一d商標/poster去紋<br />\n<br />\n算侵權 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5de3d8c17faf22538bf943e8f61e5348fe57ea4","tid":524373,"uid":31384,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T13:46:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-gEFvc1Co6BE/Tw70PyiflmI/AAAAAAAACt0/1jOAuiOBTcY/s1600/Tattoo-Gone-Wrong.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-g