ces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢幅野好撚肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T13:55:45.000Z","msg":"成隻一樣都唔算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1cf12241c1d40a63252049f4d9165ccea3e5407","tid":524373,"uid":58247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a3c90024a2012204f2ec598e4226565149a9738","tid":524373,"uid":129068,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T13:51:42.000Z","msg":"原子筆畫上去？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T13:55:46.000Z","msg":"打草稿姐"},{"pid":"b9b48d81b2e109210ba92afbb12aca639384d488","tid":524373,"uid":3698,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T13:55:52.000Z","msg":"印完上去先開始紋線，樓上兩件做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"436ec01b7a79c58298f05e6347c7e064fda6c641","tid":524373,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T13:56:32.000Z","msg":"以為係有搞笑紋身先入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dd75f1e6dc731c61d88c37486c8381160d8b015","tid":524373,"uid":62289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T14:51:59.000Z","msg":"如果條友本身係拎住張圖 去紋 <br />\n算唔算抄圖"},{"pid":"945f8f47a42c5cc3b483370dd11baa5bc179e19b","tid":524373,"uid":1774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T18:51:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好難話抄姐<br />\n<br />\n最多咪二次創作<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢幅野好撚肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>成隻一樣都唔算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連擺位都一樣"},{"pid":"390cf95bfd399bd3f88394b6c5baaf1558bdb479","tid":524373,"uid":1774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T18:56:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>純粹問下  如果係個客拎住一d商標/poster去紋<br />\n<br />\n算侵權 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又唔同 商標你個人喜好啫 你唔拎個紋身去賺錢人地都唔會理你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 亦都唔會紋poster上身啩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我講果位紋身師直接copy⼀樣 最多加少少卡通feel 但可以收人地幾萬蚊紋一個背喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實我未紋過全背我都唔係好知價錢 不過我諗應該差不多"},{"pid":"f17496f0f7d80edf533f6bdc12c8f6fa975e9c83","tid":524373,"uid":139139,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T19:20:10.000Z","msg":"老實講紋身都係嗰幾種圖案<br />\n龍鳳嗰啲就一定係抄嘅<br />\n唔通你自己作個樣落去咩<br />\n<br />\n文字就係客人俾<br />\n風格都係客人揀嘅<br />\n<br />\n如果有客人自己本來搵咗圖<br />\n咁樣都會跟返來做<br />\n<br />\n同埋要睇吓你紋幾大<br />\n如果好似你上面張相咁大<br />\n無返十萬八萬蚊都唔使旨意落樓<br />\n呢啲多數參考其他資料<br />\n可能有5-60張相一齊夾<br />\n<br />\n不過講咁多都冇撚用<br />\n最後都係要客人噏頭<br />\n客人鍾意你做乜嘢都冇用<br />\n依家客人冇要求你設計<br />\n佢就係鍾意你抄<br />\n咁你吹得脹咩<br />\n<br />\n又唔係紋係你個身到"},{"pid":"f0ad9082f5db2ebcc7e6d6365834b82a7edc465a","tid":524373,"uid":43839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T20:42:35.000Z","msg":"其實紋身係紋一世<br />\n幫你諗好哂去紋 又話抄又話唔好睇<br />\n果客諗好哂去紋 你又話易做<br />\n<br />\n咩都你地講哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dbc0540107131960c266906dbd7aa4dfba9139b","tid":524373,"uid":120070,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T20:46:09.000Z","msg":"垃圾59 <br />\n香港紋身師 唔垃圾數黎數去都係幾個 <br />\n係你啲傻仔先去紋"}]}